xyz.acygn.mokapot.wireformat

Class ObjectDescription.Size

  • java.lang.Object
    • xyz.acygn.mokapot.wireformat.ObjectDescription.Size
  • Enclosing class:
    ObjectDescription

    public static class ObjectDescription.Size
extends Object
    The size of an object description. This is measured as a number of bytes for the copiable portion, plus a number of objects for the noncopiable portion.

    ObjectDescription.Size objects are immutable, and act like value types.
